Classic Caesar Salad

10 min
$8.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyWheat

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladLight MealHealthy

Description

A fresh and crisp salad with a creamy dressing and flavorful croutons.

Ingredients

  • romaine lettuce: 1 head, chopped
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, shaved
  • croutons: 1 cup
  • caesar dressing: 1/2 cup
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
